Body: Description: Hello, I'm not able to reach the service. The Server Response with a ERR_CONNECTION_TIMED_OUT Error. The url I try to open is ryp97b8.hosted.endpointprotector.com. Thats why I could fill in the Server ID and Server Version. Could you fix this behaviour ? Best Regards Florian Cieslak

What We've Learned Updated: Could not connect to the backend, and needed to perform a restart.
Everything was fine after that.
Next Steps Updated: Ask for permission from the Devops team to connect to the backend
